        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5e7f6a355357eadd-9fd08b\"><p>之后和病人聊了五分钟后，威克格伦离开了房间。又过了五分钟，威克格伦回到房间里，病人看着他就好像之前从未见过他一样，于是两个人重新相互认识。以下的对话接着发生了：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5e7f6a355357eadd-9fd08b\"><div class=\"ref1\">\n\n    </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5e7f6a355357eadd-9fd08b\"><div class=\"ref1\"><p>“威克格伦，这是德国名字？”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000692",
