            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5e7f6a355357eadd-9fd08b\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><p><span class=\"note-b\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/5e7f6a355357eadd/text/000000867\">注</$link></span>　撒切尔原文Thatcher，作普通名词时意为盖屋匠；布什原文Bush，作普通名词时意为灌木丛。</p></div></div>"
